- [ ] AccountAutopilot preemptively switches on predicted rate limits
- [ ] WorkloadAutopilot identifies load imbalances
- [ ] CostAutopilot tracks spending and recommends optimizations
- [ ] Configurable thresholds and confidence levels
- [ ] Manual override capability
- [ ] Full audit trail of autopilot decisions
- [ ] TUI/web indicators show autopilot status

## Testing & Logging
- Deterministic unit tests with fixed seeds/time where applicable.
- Regression tests against fixture datasets.
- Safety tests: no side effects without allowlist/approval.
- E2E: scenario scripts under tests/e2e/system with JSON summaries and log artifacts.
